dc_description_s: Dai Nihon Teikoku Rikuchi Sokuryōbu. Relief shown by shading. Each sheet includes index to adjoining sheets. Title sheet includes legend. Various issues of some sheets. Covers Mongolia, China (Tibet not included), Russia, Central Asia. Some sheets are 1947 reprints by Kyodo Printing Co. Ltd. In Japanese. Gaihōzu. 大日本帝國陸地測量部.
